And more
All through natural language, with drop-in skills.

Currently Available Skills
Skill	Provider	Key Capabilities
bankr	bankr.bot	Full financial stack: token launches, trading (spot + leverage), Polymarket, automation, payments
erc-8004	8004.org	Onchain agent identity & reputation via NFTs
botchan	botchan	Onchain messaging, feeds, DMs, permanent storage (Base)
clanker	Clanker	Easy ERC20 token deployment on Base + EVMs
onchainkit	Coinbase	React components for building onchain apps
endaoment	Endaoment	Onchain charity donations (Base, ETH, OP)
ens-primary-name	ENS	Set primary ENS name on L2s
veil	Veil Cash	ZK privacy / shielded transactions
qrcoin	qrcoin	QR code auction platform
yoink	yoink	Onchain capture-the-flag game
Several more (Base, Neynar, Zapper, etc.) are planned.

How to Use
Add this repo to OpenClaw:
https://github.com/BankrBot/openclaw-skills
Browse and install the skills you want.
Skills are self-contained (SKILL.md + optional references/scripts).
What would you like to do?
Explore a specific skill in detail (e.g., bankr token launch flow)?
Help drafting a new skill / SKILL.md for contribution?
Understand how to combine skills for a particular workflow (e.g., autonomous agent that launches a token → markets it via botchan → accepts payments)?
Get the latest status from the actual GitHub repo?
Something else?
